PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of RON FOXCROFT, of Hamilton, Ontario, and OLGA BARRAT, of North Vancouver, British Columbia, as trustees of the Board of Trustees of the National Museum of Science and Technology to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years.
